channel.description: Okay, so Im using the Hybrid Pvp V2 source that has been released and working to make it my own. Right now I am adding the special attack for Korsai's sword. I have already found the gfx for the attack and added it to my server, however when i go into Itemassistant.Java and add the id of my sword to have a special bar, The special bar doesnt show up. I've tried everything and im looking for help please.
